openspec\changes\update-journal-feed-view-outliner-embed\proposal.md:24:- Make File Outliner View's editor command bridge install/uninstall based on editor focus (best-effort), so embedded outliner sessions can drive core EditorSuggest and editor commands without requiring the leaf to be a normal workspace leaf.
