id=\"19806aa8-8d11-4de1-ba9e-96b50a2221f6\">Next stage may proceed to a bounded fix design, but it should first verify the forced-rescan/remount trigger and avoid folding Reading View or undo behavior into this issue.</p></li><li class=\"not-prose space-y-2\" data-id=\"77a6e09a-0a59-420c-918f-c73d22e9ae6c\"><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"9c73183b-f476-43a0-bf73-a196e585b2cf\">Required validation: real Obsidian/CDP runtime evidence plus a regression check for returning to a previously viewed file.</p></li></ul>",
