openspec\changes\update-journal-feed-view-outliner-embed\design.md:47:File Outliner View currently installs its `workspace.activeEditor` bridge only when:
openspec\changes\update-journal-feed-view-outliner-embed\design.md:49:- AND the Outliner leaf is the active workspace leaf
openspec\changes\update-journal-feed-view-outliner-embed\design.md:51:Embedded Outliner leaves are detached and will not become `workspace.activeLeaf`, so the bridge never installs.
